  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PPLB
    This class is the subject of PPLB emulator, including all different functions of PPLB emulator.
    PPLB_BarcodeUtil
    This class provides methods for barcode related programs of the PPLB emulator.
    PPLB_FormUtil
    This class provides the method of PPLB emulator 'Form' related procedures.
    PPLB_GraphicsUtil
    This class provides methods for drawing related programs of the PPLB emulator.
    PPLB_InternalFun  
    PPLB_IOUtil
    This class provides the method of PPLB emulator printer output/input related procedures.
    PPLB_SetUtil
    This class provides methods for setting programs related to the printer parameters of the PPLB emulator.
    PPLB_TextUtil
    This class provides methods for text-related programs of the PPLB emulator.
